Maypole::View::Mason version 0.1
=====================================================

This module provides a View for Maypole using the HTML::Mason
module. See the perldoc for usage instructions. factory templates
for this view are provided in the 'templates' directory of the 
distribution.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Maypole
  HTML::Mason

